nodes.text: Squad Six was a squad of B1-series battle droids led by an OOM command battle droid. The squad was part of General Kalani's garrison on Agamar. After a skirmish against several rebels from Phoenix Cell, the Separatist holdout and the rebels ceased hostilities and fought together against the Galactic Empire. The former clone trooper Captain Rex, and Kalani came to an unofficial end to the Clone Wars by the end of the mission.
